{"tid":2309005,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"怕左支那人！為了避免被摘取 中藥植物正在演化出更好的偽裝","createTime":"2020-12-02T09:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T09:22:12.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4fe658ed8e3fd0d563edc3f64e3f4f760578468","tid":2309005,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/c38ag4v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fc38ag4v.png&h=51f7ac79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/WEBvpp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FWEBvpp2.jpg&h=266a70c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n許多動植物會演化出迷彩外觀來躲避被天敵捕食的命運，最新研究發現，人類似乎也成為<br />\n促成這些演化的壓力來源，一種經常被用於中藥的植物已經將偽裝進化的越來越隱密，為<br />\n得就是躲避人們的商業採收。<br />\n <br />\n梭砂貝母（Fritillaria delavayi）是一種多年生草本植物，主要生長於中國雲南、四川<br />\n及西藏一帶海拔 3,800 米以上的砂石地縫隙中，其鱗莖含有爐貝鹼，被認為具有鎮咳袪<br />\n痰效果，做為「川貝」來源之一在中藥中被使用了 2 千多年。<br />\n <br />\n近年由於川貝價格高漲導致商業採收增加，中國科學院昆明植物研究所和英國艾希特大學<br />\n（University of Exeter）研究發現，人們的這種過度採收似乎也促使梭砂貝母演化的更<br />\n隱密來避免被採收入藥。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/11/28/how-humans-drive-plant-evolves/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F11%2F28%2Fhow-humans-drive-plant-evolves%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOae24FYbdL6kC4fFNwqspTg%3D&h=826b07ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/11/28/how-humans-drive-plant-evolves/</a>"},{"pid":"795250ae14cb978c0b73157c42bd96db5c5e693d","tid":2309005,"uid":60977,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"污染就污染啦<br />\n<br />\n咁多籍口"},{"pid":"7afc4c1005f566d2575cac9c7cd59aadc8e945fe","tid":2309005,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"795250ae14cb978c0b73157c42bd96db5c5e693d","tid":2309005,"uid":60977,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"污染就污染啦<br />\n<br />\n咁多籍口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180881bc085f7e98cfe9511bed75d92b8c6e97d2","tid":2309005,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"795250ae14cb978c0b73157c42bd96db5c5e693d","tid":2309005,"uid":60977,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"污染就污染啦<br />\n<br />\n咁多籍口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"睇相都覺得似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}